summary:
I am passionate about using qualitative and quantitative methods to uncover underlying customer behavior and subsequently influence the design of a better user experience. I have experience with using different methodologies - AB testing, surveys, usability testing, preference testing, ...

Analytics and user research tools:
- Google Analytics 360
- Google Analytics 4
- Contentsquare
- Usertesting.com
- UsabilityHub
- Mopinion
- Hotjar
- Survey Monkey
- Screaming Frog
- SPSS

AB testing:
- VWO

Visualization tools:
- Data/Looker Studio

MS Office:
- Excel, PPT, Word
